text: "Settle" is a song by Australian singer songwriter, Vera Blue and was released on 11 March 2016. and peaked at number 79 on the Australian ARIA Chart in April 2016. A black-and-white music video was released on 3 March 2016. ==Review== Mike Wass from Idolator said the song was "dark and brooding" and "Melancholy piano propels the song along with delicate synths merely adding depth and texture." == Track listing == ;Digital download ==Charts== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" style="text-align:center" |- !
